h text-white","children":"Concept: Fueco Pizzeria"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-body text-muted max-w-[70ch]","children":"Logo, branding design, packaging & more for the concept: Fueco Pizzeria"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-3 gap-y-2 text-small text-muted","children":[["$","a",null,{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/noah.hunt.165/","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer","className":"text-text hover:text-white transition","children":"By Noah Hunt"}],[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-muted/70","children":"•"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"2025-02-21"}]],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-muted/70","children":"•"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"whitespace-nowrap","children":"3 min"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"hidden md:flex items-center gap-2","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-muted/70","children":"•"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","Concepts",{"className":"inline-flex items-center rounded-pill px-3 py-1 text-crumbs uppercase tracking-crumbs bg-white/4 text-muted shadow-tile","children":"Concepts"}]]}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid gap-card lg:grid-cols-[1fr_360px]","children":[["$","section",null,{"className":"min-w-0 space-y-card","children":[["$","hr",null,{"className":"w-full border-0 h-px bg-stroke"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none [&>h1:first-child]:mt-0 [&>h2:first-child]:mt-0 [&>h3:first-child]:mt-0 [&>ul:first-child]:mt-0 [&>ol:first-child]:mt-0 prose-headings:text-white prose-p:text-text prose-strong:text-white prose-a:text-text hover:prose-a:text-white prose-hr:border-stroke prose-code:text-white prose-pre:bg-surface prose-pre:border prose-pre:border-stroke prose-li:text-text prose-blockquote:text-text prose-blockquote:border-stroke","children":[["$","p",null,{"children":"Hello! Below you will find the full breakdown of the work I did for the concept: Fueco Pizzeria. Disclaimer: This is not a paid client project. Some areas may be underdeveloped or need more work. Thank you for taking a look!"}],"\n","$L5","\n","$L6","\n","$L7","\n","$L8","\n","$L9","\n","$La","\n","$Lb","\n","$Lc","\n","$Ld","\n","$Le","\n","$Lf","\n","$L10"]}],"$L11"]}],"$L12"]}]]}]}]],["$L13"],"$L14"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
5:["$","h2",null,{"children":"The Challenge"}]
6:["$","p",null,{"children":"To create a recognizable brand that brings the heat. Designing packaging, menus, and marketing materials that reinforce the handcrafted, wood-fired experience. Establishing a strong digital presence, including social media visuals and a logo that feel cohesive and high-end."}]
7:["$","h2",null,{"children":"Logo Design"}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"my-4","children":["Using retro typography, the shape of a classic pizza oven, and flame inspiration, I created this logo family for this concept to make its mark.\n",["$","$L15",null,{"src":"/work/fueco-pizza/1.png","alt":"The brand needed a capstone for thumbnails. By combining the fiery red that the brand uses to attract attention, set against a light tan for the main typography, it's subtle but warm.","caption":"The brand needed a capstone for thumbnails. By combining the fiery red that the brand uses to attract attention, set against a light tan for the main typography, it's subtle but warm.","zoom":true}],"\n",["$","$L15",null,{"src":"/work/fueco-pizza/2.png","alt":"This image features the logo variations Fueco could use for everything from packaging to social media. These designs unite to create a comprehensive logo family.","caption":"This image features the logo variations Fueco could use for everything from packaging to social media. These designs unite to create a comprehensive logo family.","zoom":true}]]}]
9:["$","h2",null,{"children":"Color Palette"}]
a:["$","div",null,{"className":"my-4","children":["Fueco’s colors capture the heat and intensity of wood-fired pizza. Fiery Red and Ember evoke flames and passion, while Charcoal adds depth and smokiness. Ivory provides balance, ensuring clarity and sophistication. This palette reinforces Fueco’s bold, high-energy identity at every touchpoint.\n",["$","$L15",null,{"src":"/work/fueco-pizza/3.png","alt":"In a stroke of creativity, matches were chosen to illustrate the brand's chosen color system. The flames are energetic and connect to the ethos of fire-baked pizza.","caption":"In a stroke of creativity, matches were chosen to illustrate the brand's chosen color system. The flames are energetic and connect to the ethos of fire-baked pizza.","zoom":true}]]}]
b:["$","h2",null,{"children":"Menu & Wine Packaging"}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"my-4","children":["For this section, I wanted to really give the viewer a look into what it would be like to sit and sip a glass of wine at this cozy, Italian pizzeria. I used Photoshop to add in the menu design I created for the brand and added a subtle grain to give it an \"old world\" quality. This style can be reused for all the brand imagery.\n",["$","$L15",null,{"src":"/work/fueco-pizza/4.png","alt":"In this image you will find a table setting that gives the brand a warm and homey feel. This was intentional. Adding the menu and wine list brought the idea together. This is what it would be enjoying your time at Fueco.","caption":"In this image you will find a table setting that gives the brand a warm and homey feel. This was intentional. Adding the menu and wine list brought the idea together. This is what it would be enjoying your time at Fueco.","zoom":true}],"\n",["$","$L15",null,{"src":"/work/fueco-pizza/5.png","alt":"In this mock-up two wine bottles dance together on a deep red background. For the label design, I kept it simple using the dark background and linework to create a striking contrast.","caption":"In this mock-up two wine bottles dance together on a deep red background. For the label design, I kept it simple using the dark background and linework to create a striking contrast.","zoom":true}]]}]
d:["$","h2",null,{"children":"Social Media"}]
e:["$","div",null,{"className":"my-4","children":["Fueco’s social media design embraces high-contrast visuals, bold typography, and dynamic layouts to capture attention instantly. The mix of mouthwatering food photography, strong brand elements, and vibrant red accents ensures a cohesive, scroll-stopping presence. Every post reinforces Fueco’s fiery, fast-paced energy, making the brand impossible to ignore.\n",["$","$L15",null,{"src":"/work/fueco-pizza/6.png","alt":"Alternating panels combine to provide a trendy look into the many working parts of a pizzeria. Elements of typography, custom patterns, product and lifestyle photography, and more give an energetic and cohesive vibe to their social media.","caption":"Alternating panels combine to provide a trendy look into the many working parts of a pizzeria. Elements of typography, custom patterns, product and lifestyle photography, and more give an energetic and cohesive vibe to their social media.","zoom":true}],"\n",["$","$L15",null,{"src":"/work/fueco-pizza/8.png","alt":"In this picture, Instagram post mock-ups illustrate snapshots of product photography, logo design, packaging design, and lifestyle imagery.","caption":"In this picture, Instagram post mock-ups illustrate snapshots of product photography, logo design, packaging design, and lifestyle imagery.","zoom":true}]]}]
f:["$","h2",null,{"children":"Basic Website/Application Design"}]
10:["$","div",null,{"className":"my-4","children":["Although I didn't expand on this section of the project as much as I would have liked, I used a laptop outline to throw together a quick look at what the brand's website or pizza order app could look like. Emphasis on simple line art that adds structure without distracting from the main message: DELICIOUS PIZZA!\n",["$","$L15",null,{"src":"/work/fueco-pizza/7.png","alt":"I sourced some mouthwatering product photography for this section, and I think it brought the heat. Product photography is a must for any food/beverage branding.","caption":"I sourced some mouthwatering product photography for this section, and I think it brought the heat. Product photography is a must for any food/beverage branding.","zoom":true}]]}]
